author: The Linux Foundation
description:
The State of Commercial Open Source 2025 report demonstrates how open source companies are achieving superior outcomes:

💰$26.4B raised in 2024
📈Median IPO valuations 7× higher 
🤝Median M&A valuations 14× higher 
⚡Faster progression through funding rounds 
🌐Strong correlation between community health and business value 

This research highlights the growing strength of commercial open source as both a business model and a foundation for innovation.

#OpenSource #LinuxFoundation #Innovation #Research #TechTrends #OSS #CommercialOpenSource
title: The State of Commercial Open Source 2025
